\id 2TH - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014)
\h 2 Tes
\toc3 2 Tes
\toc1 Polote Naba 2 Leta Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubaęž‰tamo Ododiyaęž‰
\toc2 2 Tesalonaika
\mt2 POLOTE NABA 2 LETA
\mt1 TESALONAIKA SOSE TAWAKALUBAęž‰TAMO
\mt2 ODODIYAęž‰
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Na Polote Sailasiko baęž‰gala Timotiko, ale laęž‰ Tesalonaika sose tawakalubaęž‰tamo baęž‰moe leta bepoememaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te aeno Nabiwi Godoko baęž‰gala Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwalo bemedenamata.
\v 2 Wadiyala Nabiwi Godoko baęž‰gala Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ibaęž‰te ibino malemale komo baęž‰gala hete komo laęž‰tamo nikalamaęž‰menaęž‰ta.
\s1 Godote Kuba Ododilipaęž‰tamo Huiya Ikalame Komo
\p 
\v 3 Aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, wadiyala hiliyonomo tetelo ale laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ Godotamo kalakala tabo baęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakomaęž‰. Iyo, ale baęž‰ba kaęž‰na kewagelenamaęž‰ baęž‰moe baęž‰ hido komola, mabu laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komote ba apepehona, laęž‰ ipuwalo etapaęž‰te etapi malemalelo demalagidolenama baęž‰be komote atumu komaęž‰ nedaęž‰na.
\v 4 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale komo Godokono sose tawakalubaęž‰tamo daęž‰nikulinakomaęž‰, ibi ipuwalo laęž‰ ba awagaminale laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komomaęž‰ gaęž‰lanakomaęž‰. Iyo, hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te laęž‰tamo koko temeteme dikalamena laęž‰ huiyatiya baęž‰be menemene ipuwalo Godoko hibimaęž‰ midi mabumaęž‰ kodakodalo daęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanama, ale baęž‰be komomaęž‰ komo hibimaęž‰ midipi konomamo baęž‰bemaęž‰ kiyalamenakomaęž‰.
\p 
\v 5 Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰le temeteme uwate tetelo kodakodalo daęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanama, baęž‰be komote baęž‰moe komo behawakalimina, Godote hopo habanapino kuba ododili komokomo danagilamelelamemene ebete baęž‰be komo tuputupunomolo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kododimaęž‰ne, ebete laęž‰eno temeteme uwate mabumaęž‰ laęž‰ ebeno hidohido gaęž‰limapi gugudimaęž‰ ba kaęž‰lami, modobo tabo baęž‰bo kogoemaęž‰ne laęž‰le ebeno Ko Gawadubu habamo konaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰hamaęž‰.
\v 6 Iyo, Godoko baęž‰ tuputupu komokomo kapiya ododilidawala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te baęž‰ma tetelo temeteme laęž‰tamo dikalamena ebete ibaęž‰tamo kuba huiya kikalamemaęž‰ne,
\v 7 huiyatiya ebete laęž‰godone baęž‰gala agodone aeno temeteme komo hiliyonomo gobogobamo ba miyaęž‰te a kapimilo baęž‰bo kogelebadiaęž‰memaęž‰ne.
\p Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰ba tetelo aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰suti ebeno helonomo nopopaęž‰go Hunu Habane hawakala daęž‰pemene,
\v 8 puyaęž‰te ebeno Hido Tabamo papamilaęž‰haheno baęž‰gala Godoko ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, ebete baęž‰bi tawakalubaęž‰tamo helonomo powagoeno koaęž‰mo huiya baęž‰bo kopikalamemaęž‰ne.
\v 9 Baęž‰bene baęž‰bi kuba ododilipino temeteme komote itana itana tetelo bitanamene, iyo, Kodawate ibi ebeno holoholo hapuni baęž‰gala ebeno helonomo aęž‰laęž‰mina alone tamaęž‰mo baęž‰ dito koelamemaęž‰ne ibaęž‰te ibino kuba huiya ipuwalo konemedehonamaęž‰.
\v 10 Huiyatiya kalakala konomola, Kodawate ebeno Ko Hegelalo daęž‰pemene, baęž‰ba tetelo puyaęž‰te ebeno tawakalubimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana baęž‰bi hibimaęž‰ midipi hiliyonomate ebe hunamo ba adipate ebe mabumaęž‰ konomamo kohanohanohomaęž‰naęž‰! Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le baęž‰bi tawakalubino konomo kapiyuimi ipuwalo atumu kopolaęž‰namaęž‰nemata, mabu ale laęž‰tamo ebeno Hido Tabo daęž‰polamagimimaęž‰ laęž‰ baęž‰be tabo hibimaęž‰ aęž‰midimata.
\p 
\v 11 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale baęž‰be komo ba emalagidolo komo hiliyonomo tetelo laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ aeno Godotamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na toetoehonakomaęž‰, ebete kebe hido emede komomaęž‰ laęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰lami, wadiyala ebete baęž‰be emede ipuwalo laęž‰ ebeno hidohido gaęž‰limapi gugudimaęž‰ naęž‰midilaęž‰menaęž‰ta, baęž‰gala wadiyala ebete ebeno helo laęž‰tamo nikalamaęž‰menaęž‰ta, laęž‰le laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno hidohido ubi komone baęž‰gala laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwane tuputupu ododili komo ba uluhukulatele baęž‰bi komo hidamo kupulaęž‰lemaęž‰.
\v 12 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ puyaęž‰te laęž‰eno hidohido emede komokomo dulamemenaęž‰, ibaęž‰te aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰suku awagaminalo ebeno mahilo hunamo ba adipate, baęž‰be hido awagaha komote Yaęž‰sugodone laęž‰tamo atumu kakapuluhukumaęž‰ne, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala baęž‰moe hido komote aeno Godo baęž‰gala Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ibino malemale ipuwado baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na nuluhukamene.
\c 2
\s1 Baęž‰moe Hopo Habalo Koko Kuba Ododilidawate Komahigamaęž‰ne
\p 
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu pe tetelo ebete a hibimaęž‰ midipi ebaęž‰go kemedenamaęž‰ daęž‰pekapiyuiaęž‰memene, baęž‰be komomaęž‰ ale laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kiyalamaęž‰ta,
\v 2 puyaęž‰te haęž‰da amiho tabo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na daęž‰gaęž‰lana, â€śKodawoeno Ko Hegelate yaęž‰lo uluhukui,â€ť baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰eno ukuiti gagagagamaęž‰ akedaęž‰halaęž‰ baęž‰gala laęž‰ ukui bilibili komo akalawaęž‰laęž‰. Diyala, laęž‰ ipuwalo komopaęž‰te daęž‰ naęž‰gaęž‰lana baęž‰moe tabo komote agodone pi. Ao, eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰! Ale dopamo laęž‰godolo ba pemede laęž‰tamo Godokono ukui daęž‰hawakaliminakuimaęž‰ baęž‰gala komo tetelo ale tabo dito daęž‰gaęž‰lanakuimaęž‰, baęž‰gala ale galane dopo leta laęž‰tamo daęž‰poemimaęž‰, baęž‰bi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tete hiliyonomolo baęž‰mako tabote agodone kuluhukuhaęž‰.
\p 
\v 3 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ komopino haęž‰da amiho tabo komokomo hibimaęž‰ akamidilaęž‰laęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, Yaęž‰sukunu pe hegelate uluhukuhino, dopamo hopo habanapi hiliyonomate Godokono hibi gabo ba miyaęž‰pa Koko Kuba Ododilidawate baęž‰bo komahigamaęž‰ne. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰be dawate Saitanakono Koe Habalo kuba huiya hibinomolo kolawemaęž‰ne,
\v 4 mabu a hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te hibi Godomaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰minakomaęž‰ ebete baęž‰be Kodawa hibihaęž‰maęž‰ kogoemaęž‰ne. Baęž‰gala komo hopo habanapaęž‰te hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ idaęž‰daęž‰lino gobogobo dadikulamenaka, ebete ibino adikulame komokomo hiliyonomo ba duhilame ebe haęž‰kiya ebe hunamo adipatelo baęž‰bo kogoemaęž‰ne, â€śNa baęž‰ Godotela, na hopo lumagihaęž‰!â€ť Iyo, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete hibi Godo Adikumino Hiyaęž‰ Genamalo ba luta, tawakalubi hiliyonomo baęž‰bo kokiyahalamemaęž‰ne ibaęž‰te ebe kapiya kadikumimaęž‰.
\p 
\v 5 Baęž‰ hibila, nale dopamo komo hegelalo laęž‰godolo ba pemede baęž‰moi komokomo laęž‰ iyaęž‰tulamimata, huiyatiya wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰ma tetelo naeno tabo komokomo gala naęž‰kemalagidolaęž‰laęž‰.
\v 6 Laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala, baęž‰ma tetelo hopo habalo etoeno helote Koko Kuba Ododilidawoeno komo naęž‰duhimina, iyo, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godokono ubi tete peheno baęž‰be dawate aęž‰kamahigamene.
\v 7 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰ma tetelo kebe helote Kubadawoeno mahiga komo daęž‰duhimina, Godote baęž‰be helo tamaęž‰mo ihateheno Kubadawate diya gabodo hopo konomolo ebeno oko bowatina, iyo, ebete baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ebeno kuba ododili komo yaęž‰lo aęž‰tupuimiyaęž‰.
\v 8 Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, galane baęž‰be dawoeno kuba komote tawakalubaęž‰tamo hawakalanomo kohawakalamaęž‰ne, baęž‰bene Godote kebe tete ebetamo dikamemene, baęž‰be tete wibote Kodawa Yaęž‰suti pete ebeno tabone daęž‰puluhukumini baęž‰be dehaęž‰potonomo tabo kapiyamo baęž‰be Kubadawa baęž‰ dito kopanakapumimaęž‰ne.
\p 
\v 9 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ niyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰, baęž‰moe Kubadawate daęž‰pemene, ebete hiliyonomo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hanohano komo baęž‰gala tole komo Saitanakono konomo heloamo kopododilimaęž‰ne hopo habanapi haęž‰da kopamiholamemaęž‰.
\v 10 Iyo, ibi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te Godoko hibimaęž‰ midihino dito daęž‰haęž‰lahamenaęž‰, ibaęž‰te haęž‰lahaheno dopamo Kubadawate hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ haęž‰da amiho gabodo ibi ibino olalati kuititaęž‰mo komagatalemaęž‰ne. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰bi tawakalubaęž‰te Godokono hibi komo kalakalago naęž‰lawiyaęž‰tale Godote ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ baęž‰mulaęž‰lelamiyaęž‰naęž‰, huiyatiya ibaęž‰te baęž‰be komo ko komomaęž‰ kagaęž‰luyaęž‰haęž‰ baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te hibilo kokubakubahamaęž‰naęž‰.
\v 11 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te hibi komo lawehaęž‰ mabumaęž‰ Godote ibaęž‰tamo Haęž‰da Amihodawa oememaęž‰ modobomaęž‰ goena. Baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ibaęž‰te baęž‰be dawoeno helo komamo guditi ebeno haęž‰da tabo komokomo hibimaęž‰ komidilimaęž‰naęž‰,
\v 12 iyo, hopo habanapi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te Godokono hibi komo laweheno ibino kateneno ubilo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba komo kalakalago dododilina, ebete ibi hiliyonomoeno komokomo anagilamelelamete ibaęž‰tamo kuba huiya baęž‰bo kikalamemaęž‰ne.
\s1 Godote Hibimaęž‰ Midipino Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Komulaęž‰lemaęž‰ Ibi Duwatiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, wadiyala hiliyonomo tetelo ale laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ kalakala tabo Godotamo baęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakomaęž‰. Hibila, ebete laęž‰ malemalelo demalagidolena, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ebete baęž‰moe hopo tupuimi mabuni laęž‰ uwatiyaęž‰ta, laęž‰le ebeno komo hibimaęž‰ ba midi ebeno Gobogobote laęž‰ talonapimaęž‰ midiliti laęž‰le kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo baęž‰bo kolawemaęž‰.
\v 14 Iyo, ale Hido Tabo laęž‰tamo dolamagimimaęž‰ Godote baęž‰be komodo laęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰lamiaęž‰ta, laęž‰le komo hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰go Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono helonomo alo ipuwalo kemedenamaęž‰.
\v 15 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale Godokono tabo olamagimi ipuwalo baęž‰gala aeno dopo leta ipuwalo laęž‰ kebe komokomo kiyaęž‰tulametanakui, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bi komo hibilo ba watilaęž‰motaęž‰na kodakodalo naęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanalaęž‰.
\p 
\v 16-17 Numaęž‰laęž‰, yaęž‰lo tetenomolo aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisote aeno Nabiwi Godokobaęž‰ a konomamo ba emalagidoloena, ibaęž‰te ibino malemale ipuwado a emedena teteno tepo ipuwoeno helo atamo ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰ ale Yaęž‰sukunu pe kuititaęž‰mo uliholo kolatiminamaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala ibaęž‰te baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na laęž‰eno tepo ipuwa naęž‰heluilamenakamenaęž‰, hiliyonomo tetelo hidohido komate laęž‰eno tabo gaęž‰la ipuwane baęž‰gala ododili ipuwane kopikulinakomaęž‰.
\c 3
\s1 Tesalonaika Sose Tawakalubaęž‰te Polui Mabumaęž‰ Godoko Kotoemehomaęž‰ Polote Ibi Daęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe leta kuititi hapulu ale laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kiyalamaęž‰ta, wadiyala laęž‰ toetoe tabamo a Godotamo naęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰tiyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu a ubila Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu tabote aeno oko ipuwado komo hiliyonomo hopo tawakalubaęž‰tamo tiyonomolo kotomaęž‰, baęž‰gala a ubila ulihopaęž‰te baęž‰be tabo ba milimiho Godotamo kalakala tabo kadipatemaęž‰, laęž‰le dopamo ebeno tabo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰lawiuima baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.
\v 2 Baęž‰bene wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰moe eta komomaęž‰ Godoko naęž‰katoemehuyaęž‰laęž‰, ebete koko kuba ododilipi dubuino helo ipuwane aeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰leaęž‰memaęž‰, mabu komo hopo habanapaęž‰te Godokono tabo uliho tetelo hibimaęž‰ kamidinahaęž‰.
\p 
\v 3 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kalakala konomola, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi mabumaęž‰ Kodawate atumu laęž‰ ba heluilame, Saitanakono alaholoho ododili ipuwalo laęž‰ ebete kitaguaęž‰midalemaęž‰naęž‰ta! Iyo, aeno Kodawa baęž‰ Hibidawanomola!
\v 4 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ a iyaęž‰tawahala ale kebe hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komomaęž‰ laęž‰ daęž‰kiyalamenaka, laęž‰ baęž‰bi komokomo ododili ipuwalo ba polaęž‰na baęž‰bi komo dito aęž‰kamiyaęž‰palaęž‰mata. Numaęž‰laęž‰, Kodawate laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ baęž‰be hido ukui atamo nikaaęž‰mena, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ukui bilibili komote agodolo kitanahaęž‰.
\v 5 Wadiyala laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midi gabodo ba tolame, Kodawa Kelisote laęž‰ dopalamete temeteme ikuliho tetelo ebete ebeno kodakodalo utitata komago baęž‰gala Godokono malemale emalagidolo komago laęž‰ naęž‰magatalenakamenaęž‰ta.
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Oko Nowatinamenaęž‰ Ibi Haęž‰kiya Ibino Modobohaęž‰ Komokomo Kulamemaęž‰
\p 
\v 6 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ aeno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰laęž‰, ale aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono mahilamo laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kiyalamaęž‰ta, laęž‰ ipuwalo puyaęž‰te aeno iyaęž‰tulame komamo papamilaęž‰haleheno baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te ibi haęž‰kiya owalubilimaęž‰ buhamamaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bako hibimaęž‰ midipino ododili ipuwamo akogomalaęž‰.
\v 7 Iyo, ale laęž‰ ipuwalo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰pemedimaęž‰ laęž‰ baęž‰be komo iyaęž‰tawahanomola, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ atu ododili ipuwalo nemedenalaęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ale oko owatimaęž‰ buhamamaęž‰ edaęž‰haheno,
\v 8 du baęž‰gala hegela hiliyonomolo aeno kokotamo menemene oko owatihonakuimaęž‰ a haęž‰kiya aeno modobohaęž‰ komokomo kulamemaęž‰, baęž‰bene baęž‰be gabodo ale eta lumagigodone baaęž‰ malemalelo dito kalawenakuihaęž‰, ao, a ebetamo aęž‰huiyanakuimaęž‰.
\v 9 Baęž‰ hibila, Godokono okopaęž‰te ibino modobohaęž‰ komokomo ipuwalo hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰godone ilina baęž‰gala mani uwatemaęž‰ talona kitanahaęž‰, huiyatiya ale laęž‰go ba emedena baęž‰ba kaęž‰na kewagelenakuihaęž‰, mabu a ubi bihatimaęž‰ laęž‰tamo eta hido go hawakalimiti, laęž‰le oko owati ipuwalo aeno ododili komo kotaęž‰matalemaęž‰.
\v 10 Baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na aęž‰kiyalamiaęž‰ta, â€śKebe lumagiti oko owati ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰mene, wadiyala komopaęž‰te ebetamo baaęž‰ akikamaęž‰laęž‰.â€ť
\p 
\v 11 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, ale baęž‰moe komomaęž‰ laęž‰ gala naęž‰kakiyalamaęž‰ta mabu tabote atamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na puluhukui, laęž‰ ipuwalo komopaęž‰te oko owatimaęž‰ buhamamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰ha, ibi haęž‰kiya ibino hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komo ulameheno ibino tabo gaęž‰la ipuwalo puyaęž‰te hibi oko komokomo dowatihona ibaęž‰tamo temeteme baęž‰bo ikalamenaka.
\v 12 Iyo, ale baęž‰bako tawakalubi ba tutumulatele Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono mahilamo ibi koamo kiyahalamemaęž‰, ibaęž‰te tabo gaęž‰la ipuwalo komo tawakalubaęž‰tamo temeteme ikalameheno, huiyatiya ibaęž‰te hegehege mani oko owatiho ipuwalo ibi haęž‰kiya ibino modobohaęž‰ komokomo nulamenakamenaęž‰.
\p 
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ekakaęž‰laęž‰, kalakala konomola, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo hidohido komo kododilimaęž‰ helohaęž‰maęž‰ akedaęž‰halaęž‰.
\v 14 Baęž‰gala laęž‰ ipuwalo eta lumagiti baęž‰moe leta taboeno iyaęž‰tulame komamo papamiwata ubihaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰lo oko owatihino dito daęž‰lutamene, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bako lumagino kuba komo kohawakalimimaęž‰ ebeno ododili ipuwalo ebaęž‰go akakapiyalaęž‰. Diyala, baęž‰moe gabodo ebete hilopo lawete ebeno kuba ukui komone Godotamo gala daęž‰ kohobigamene,
\v 15 huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, ebete ukui hiyaęž‰maęž‰ tiyolo midihino ebe laęž‰go alaholodawamaęž‰ akamidaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le huiyatiya ebe laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ekawimaęž‰ kaęž‰milo ebeno tepo ipuwoeno kuba ukui komomaęž‰ ebe malemalelo naęž‰kiyamiyaęž‰laęž‰.
\s1 Polote Leta Kuititi Hapulu Tabo Komokomo Dolamagiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 16 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hete atamo dikaaęž‰mena, wadiyala baęž‰be Kodawate laęž‰ hiliyonomagodolo ba emedena hiliyonomo tetelo ebe haęž‰kiya laęž‰eno hiliyonomo komokomo ipuwalo ebeno hete laęž‰tamo nikalamenakamenaęž‰ta.
\p 
\v 17 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe leta kuititi hapulu na Polote naeno mahilo baęž‰gala nolata tabo naeno kokotonomamo miyaęž‰temo, eta lumagiti baęž‰moe kuititi tabo kamiyaęž‰tehaęž‰. Iyo, baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno kokotola, naeno leta hiliyonomo ododili ipuwalo na haęž‰kiya naeno mahilo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na miyaęž‰tenakomo.
\p 
\v 18 Wadiyala aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono malemale komote laęž‰ hiliyonomagodolo nitanamene. Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la. 
